#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:49
msgid ""
"This decorative block is like a huge mushroom stem, but with the stem "
"texture on all sides."
msgstr ""
"Dekorazio-bloke hau onddo-zurtoin handi bat bezalakoa da, baina zurtoinaren "
"ehundura alde guztietan du."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:107
msgid ""
"By placing huge mushroom blocks of the same species next to each other, the "
"sides that touch each other will turn into pores permanently."
msgstr ""
"Espezie bereko onddo-bloke handiak bata bestearen ondoan jartzean, ukitzen "
"diren aldeak poro bihurtuko dira etengabe."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:166
msgid ""
"Huge red mushroom blocks are the cap parts of huge red mushrooms. It "
"consists of a red skin and can have pores on each of its sides."
msgstr ""
"Onddo gorrien bloke izugarriak dira onddo gorri handien estalkiaren zatiak. "
"Larruazal gorri bat da, eta poroak izan ditzake alde bakoitzean."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:167
msgid "The stem part of a huge red mushroom."
msgstr "Perretxiko gorri handi baten zurtoinaren zatia."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:168
msgid "Huge Red Mushroom Block"
msgstr "Perretxiko gorrizko blokea"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:168
msgid "Huge Red Mushroom Stem"
msgstr "Perretxiko gorriaren zurtoina"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:168
msgid "Huge Red Mushroom All-Faces Stem"
msgstr "Perretxiko gorriaren zurtoina (aurpegi guztiak)"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:171
msgid ""
"Huge brown mushroom blocks are the cap parts of huge brown mushrooms. It "
"consists of a brown skin and can have pores on each of its sides."
msgstr ""
"Braune Riesenpilzblöcke sind die Kappenteile von braunen Riesenpilzen. Sie "
"bestehen aus einer braunen Haut und können Poren an jede ihrer seiten haben."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:172
msgid "The stem part of a huge brown mushroom."
msgstr "Der Stängelteil eines braunen Riesenpilzes."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:173
msgid "Huge Brown Mushroom Block"
msgstr "Perretxiko marroizko blokea"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:173
msgid "Huge Brown Mushroom Stem"
msgstr "Perretxiko marroiaren zurtoina"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/huge.lua:173
msgid "Huge Brown Mushroom All-Faces Stem"
msgstr "Perretxiko marroiaren zurtoina (Aurpegi guztiak)"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:20
msgid ""
"Brown mushrooms are fungi which grow and spread in darkness, but are "
"sensitive to light. They are inedible as such, but they can be used to craft "
"food items."
msgstr ""
"Onddo marroiak iluntasunean hazten eta hedatzen diren onddoak dira, baina "
"argiarekiko sentikorrak dira. Ez dira jangarriak, baina elikagaiak egiteko "
"erabil daitezke."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:21
msgid ""
"Red mushrooms are fungi which grow and spread in darkness, but are sensitive "
"to light. They are inedible as such, but they can be used to craft food "
"items."
msgstr ""
"Onddo gorriak iluntasunean hazten eta hedatzen diren onddoak dira, baina "
"argiarekiko sentikorrak dira. Ez dira jangarriak, baina elikagaiak egiteko "
"erabil daitezke."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:23
msgid ""
"A single mushroom of this species will slowly spread over time towards a "
"random solid opaque block with a light level of 12 or lower in a 3×3×3 cube "
"around the mushroom. It stops spreading when there are 5 or more mushrooms "
"of the same species within an area of 9×3×9 blocks around the mushroom."
msgstr ""
"Espezie horretako onddo bakar bat pixkanaka zabalduko da ausazko bloke opaku "
"solido aleatorio baterantz, 3 × 3 × 3 × 3ko kuboan 12 argi edo gutxiagoko "
"argi-mailarekin, onddoaren inguruan. Gelditzen da espezie bereko 5 onddo edo "
"gehiago daudenean 9 × 3 × 9 blokeko eremu batean onddoaren inguruan."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:24
msgid ""
"Mushrooms will eventually uproot at a light level of 12 or higher. On "
"mycelium or podzol, they survive and spread at any light level."
msgstr ""
"Onddoak 12 argi edo gehiagoko mailan deserrotuko dira. Micelio edo podsol "
"hizkuntzan, biziraun egiten dute eta edozein argi mailatan hedatzen dira."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:26
msgid "Grows on podzol, mycelium and other blocks"
msgstr "Podsol, micelio eta beste bloke batzuetan hazten da"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:26
msgid "Spreads in darkness"
msgstr "Iluntasunean hedatzen da"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:28
msgid ""
"This mushroom can be placed on mycelium and podzol at any light level. It "
"can also be placed on blocks which are both solid and opaque, as long as the "
"light level at daytime is not higher than 12."
msgstr ""
"Onddo hori mikelio eta podsol gainean jar daiteke, edozein argi mailatan. "
"Bloke solido eta opakuetan ere jar daiteke, betiere egunean zehar argi-maila "
"12 baino handiagoa ez bada."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:92 mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:150
msgid "Brown Mushroom"
msgstr "Perretxiko marroia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:121
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:156
msgid "Red Mushroom"
msgstr "Perretxiko gorria"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:161
msgid "Mushroom Stew"
msgstr "Perretxiko erregosia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_mushrooms/small.lua:162
msgid ""
"Mushroom stew is a healthy soup which can be consumed to restore some hunger "
"points."
msgstr ""
"Perretxiko erregosia zopa osasungarria da, eta gose-puntu batzuk "
"lehengoratzeko kontsumi daiteke."
